description: This Alexa skill's purpose is to bring a fencing 101 course to the hands of anyone who owns an Amazon Alexa. Some technique is explained together with defining the parts of the weapons, the rules and offensive/defensive strategies. Moving forward, Alexa's repertoire will continue to grow to have a broader knowledge of the sport.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask fencing master what's a blade
name: fencing master
shortDescription: Simple How-to for certain fencing moves, including some definitions for technical terms.
